HEADWORD: Paphian
<hw>Pa"phi*an</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>Paphius</ets>, Gr. <?/, from <?/ the city Paphos.]</ety> <def>Of or
